# Log4j CVE-2021-44228
## Lessons learned
On December 1st 2021 I completed an intensive 24-week long boot camp dedicated to CyberSecurity.
Cybersecurity bootcamp, a few days later log4j (CVE-2021-44228) vulnearability was found.

The resulting flood of information has given me the opportunity to see how the industry works and spark better understanding of how CyberSecurity practioners
do their job.

The guiding question in my research is what would my CISO want me to be doing?
